"replyTime":"2020-12-31T10:57:47.000Z","msg":"咁應該真係嬲左你送公仔<br />\n可能佢本身對你份禮物好大期望<br />\n有D男人好現實<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n俾你參考下:<br />\n有個男仔朋友話本身期望個女朋友搞D生日驚喜, 高級餐廳, 加名貴禮物<br />\n點知個女仔送份禮物只值幾百蚊, 加上食餐飯好普通<br />\n嬲得滯分左手"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T11:03:18.000Z","msg":"樓主送得公仔應該好細個？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n男仔唔鍾意呢啲都正常<br />\n但佢反應真係幾衰下<br />\n平時都唔重視你㗎？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T12:42:54.000Z","msg":"咁要問過樓主先知"},{"pid":"c6bfb22231db36ec5e9b099cead5387afe0913ab","tid":2347822,"uid":2419,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ef3b7b31746e88f7ad9f2b6c8cfb9349fa500fab","tid":2347822,"uid":207879,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"83f2789ce8a1ff35a287ae0c45cec9bc64337a81","tid":2347822,"uid":142522,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T10:35:10.000Z","msg":"你同佢一齊咗幾耐？<br />\nbtw, 男人應該有八成都好討厭唔實用 只有紀念價值嘅禮物<br />\n但係佢咁講嘢又有啲奇怪<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T11:15:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T12:46:59.000Z","msg":"算鳩數啦 佢想屌你咋"},{"pid":"9111ce2827971cb81d53f653a9a6743a1de72221","tid":2347822,"uid":129506,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T12:56:01.000Z","msg":"樓主都幾撚犯賤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n擺明條仔有問題，就算幾唔鐘意都起碼會拆開禮物交下戲，基本禮貌都要<br />\n<br />\n樓主仲要係到反省自己做錯咩，你老母生你出黎俾條仔當免費雞屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd4c29a102a3824152bfa53fea7464fbcc78b9a5","tid":2347822,"uid":155818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T12:57:31.000Z","msg":"送錯左比人?"},{"pid":"16f2845af14b363e95a62fd903f76d21fd7b916a","tid":2347822,"uid":155818,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T12:58:09.000Z","msg":"男人老狗咁鳩小氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2bb4cf8d213054da83f2d7290fb20d0b5412a13c","tid":2347822,"uid":250491,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T13:05:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"773ec6f3822b3fbf182e04e7f7ab38d6bdd1233f","tid":2347822,"uid":304228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T13:09:00.000Z","msg":"樓主好慘 精心準備禮物<br />\n但男朋友好似無表達返你期待嘅反應<br />\n<br />\n可能份禮物真係唔太適合佢啦<br />\n始終你地剛開始無耐<br />\n呢啲要磨合嘅<br />\n<br />\n佢唔係討厭你送<br />\n但純粹個人唔慣收禮物 （男仔之間好少收禮）<br />\n而你整嘅嘢佢又覺得無咩用 只可以擺喺度<br />\n<br />\n（所以送嘢俾人下次可以了解多少少對方脾性！）<br />\n<br />\n唔好灰心<br />\n你都可以適當表達返你感受<br />\n唔好俾呢件事影響咗大家真誠相處"}]}